        <mxCell id="af2" value="&lt;b&gt;Audit Table&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Timestamp | User | Action&lt;br&gt;Resource | Status | Details&lt;br&gt;Timeline-style display&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontFamily=Segoe UI;fontSize=11;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="a_feat">
